### Create a Product
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Name": "Laptop",
  "Price": 1500
}

### Search a Product
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/search?Name=Laptop

### Paginate Products
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?page=1&limit=5

### Filter Products
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/filter?minPrice=1000&maxPrice=2000&Name=Laptop
